openbrowser (0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * Multi-tab browsing with pinned, private, and muted tabs
  * GNOME-style gray UI with libadwaita
  * Built-in download manager
  * Bookmark manager with folders and import/export
  * History manager with search
  * Privacy features: ad blocker, tracker blocker, HTTPS only
  * Developer tools integration
  * Keyboard shortcuts
  * Settings with JSON persistence

 -- OpenBrowser Team <openbrowser@example.com>  Sun, 14 Jun 2026 12:00:00 +0000
